claim.claim-text:
1. A golf club shaft selecting system, comprising:
head speed detecting means for detecting a head speed at impact in a swing of a golfer;
swing tempo detecting means for detecting a swing tempo of said golfer;
a chart indicative of a preferable shaft flex point corresponding to said head speed and said swing tempo;
selecting means for selecting a golf club shaft suitable for said golfer referring to said chart and based on said head speed and swing tempo detected by said head speed detecting means and said swing tempo detecting means; and
displaying means for displaying the golf club shaft selected by said selecting means.

4. A golf club shaft selecting system, comprising:
head speed detecting means for detecting a head speed at impact in a swing of a golfer;
swing tempo detecting means for detecting a swing tempo of said golfer;
a first chart indicative of a preferable shaft mass corresponding to said head speed and said swing tempo;
a second chart indicative of a preferable shaft flex point corresponding to said head speed and said swing tempo;
selecting means for selecting a golf club shaft suitable for said golfer referring to said firs and second charts and based on said head speed and swing temp detected by said head speed detecting means and said swing tempo detecting means; and
displaying means for displaying the golf club shaft selected by said selecting means.
